# Privacy Policy for Easy Quran

**Effective Date:** October 2025  

Welcome to **Easy Quran** (‚Äúwe‚Äù, ‚Äúour‚Äù, or ‚Äúus‚Äù).  
Your privacy is very important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use the **Easy Quran** mobile application.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

### a. Information You Provide  
We do **not** require any account registration or personal data to use Easy Quran.  
If you contact us for support or feedback, we may collect the information you voluntarily share, such as your name and email address.

### b. Automatically Collected Information  
The app may collect limited, non-personal data to improve performance, such as:
- Device model and OS version  
- App version and crash logs  
- Anonymous usage analytics (if enabled)  

This data helps us enhance app stability and user experience.

### c. No Sensitive Data  
We **do not** collect or store any religious, biometric, or financial information.

---

## 2. How We Use Information

Collected information (if any) is used solely to:
- Improve the app‚Äôs design, functionality, and performance  
- Identify and fix technical issues  
- Respond to user requests and feedback  

We **never** sell, rent, or share your information for advertising or tracking.

---

## 3. Data Storage and Security

- All Quran text, translations, and tafseer data are stored **locally** on your device.  
- No personal information is transmitted to our servers.  
- Temporary preferences (e.g., theme, last-read verse) remain only on your device.  
- We take reasonable measures to keep your data secure and private.

---

## 4. Third-Party Services

To ensure quality and performance, Easy Quran may use trusted third-party tools:
- **Google Play Services** ‚Äì app updates & delivery  
- **Firebase Analytics / Crashlytics** ‚Äì crash reports & anonymous performance metrics  

These tools may collect limited technical data as per their policies:
- [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)  
- [Firebase Privacy Policy](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)

---

## 5. Children‚Äôs Privacy

Easy Quran is safe for **all ages**.  
We do not collect or request personal data from children under 13.  
The app contains **no ads**, **no tracking**, and **no in-app purchases**.

---

## 6. Links to External Sources

The app may include references or links to external Quran repositories or resources.  
We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of external websites.

